1. Creating and Renaming Files/Directories
mkdir test_dir  #creates directory with name test_dir

cd test_dir  #Changing directory to test_dir 
touch example.txt   #creating empty file named example.txt
mv example.txt renamed_example.txt  #renaming the same file with mv command to renamed_example.txt


